data.text:
An original 2000 UK Quad poster for the feature film spin-off from the popular character’s of Harry Enfield’s TV series and follows the teenage pair as they go on holiday to Ibiza in the hope of becoming superstar DJ’s and meeting girls.

Film Category: Comedy

Actor / Actresses: Harry Enfield, Kathy Burke & Rhys Ifans

Poster Type: UK Quad 30 x 40"

Condition: Very Good, folded, some wear to folds and border

Year: 2000
